reviewText: only watched 15 min before turned off--so bad it's painful
Bad acting, awful filming. Maybe the five star review was by someone who was in it.

The theme of the movie was not bad but the sound quality was terrible. There were times when you could not understand what was being said because of background noise. Also, it kept stopping to buffer every few minutes which made it hard to watch.
So bad! So dumb! It was painful to watch!  Bad acting, bad plot and character development, bad filming, bad music, bad everything.  Absolutely horrible!!
Jaimie Steck was amazing in this movie.  A real natural!!!!  Enjoyed this movie!!!!
